      <title>米莱在互相侮辱后提议与卢拉会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/milei-proposes-encounter-with-lula-after-mutual-insults</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱向巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦伸出了橄榄枝，他多次称他为“共产主义者”，提议举行会晤以解冻邻国之间的高层关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/milei-proposes-encounter-with-lula-after-mutual-insults</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 22:52:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔总统诺博亚因电力危机关闭国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/ecuador-president-noboa-shuts-down-nation-on-electricity-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺博亚下令企业和政府办公室周四和周五关闭，原因是在周日举行的重要全国公投之前严重缺乏电力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/ecuador-president-noboa-shuts-down-nation-on-electricity-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 21:39:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国因安全风险考虑对境外投资实施新限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/uk-mulls-new-curbs-on-outward-investment-over-security-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国正在考虑对人工智能和半导体等新兴技术的对外投资实施新的限制，理由是援助俄罗斯和中国等敌对国家存在潜在的安全风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/uk-mulls-new-curbs-on-outward-investment-over-security-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯建设新的亚洲贸易路线以削弱战争制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/russia-builds-new-asia-trade-routes-to-weaken-sanctions-over-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯正在加紧建设两条连接亚洲和欧洲的新运输走廊，寻求削弱对其乌克兰战争的制裁，同时中东动荡扰乱了全球贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/russia-builds-new-asia-trade-routes-to-weaken-sanctions-over-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称中国“仇外”，加剧2024年竞选言辞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/biden-calls-china-xenophobic-ramping-up-campaign-rhetoric</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统在摇摆州宾夕法尼亚州的竞选活动中，称中国为“仇外者”，同时强调了这个亚洲国家的经济困境，试图证明美国的经济实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/biden-calls-china-xenophobic-ramping-up-campaign-rhetoric</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:55:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马约卡斯弹劾案在参议院失败，挫败了共和党的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/mayorkas-impeachment-dies-in-senate-thwarting-republican-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，共和党领导的罢免国土安全部长亚历杭德罗·马约卡斯的行动遭遇了虎头蛇尾但可以预见的命运，因为参议院迅速搁置了对他的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/mayorkas-impeachment-dies-in-senate-thwarting-republican-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:18:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着剥离或禁令投票临近，TikTok 面临华盛顿清算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-moving-on-fast-track-through-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 即将在华盛顿迎来关键时刻，国会正在快速批准一项法案，旨在迫使该社交媒体平台的中国母公司字节跳动有限公司剥离其有争议的所有权股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-moving-on-fast-track-through-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:26:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克罗地亚总理普伦科维奇在激烈的选举中遭遇挫折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/croatia-s-plenkovic-may-lose-majority-in-vote-exit-polls-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚总理安德烈·普连科维奇在紧张的全国选举中遭遇挫折，因为他面临总统佐兰·米拉诺维奇的挑战，后者嘲笑对乌克兰的军事援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/croatia-s-plenkovic-may-lose-majority-in-vote-exit-polls-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软认为俄罗斯业务放缓，中国影响投票的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/microsoft-sees-slowdown-in-russia-china-efforts-to-sway-us-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司的最新研究显示，俄罗斯正在努力在 2024 年大选前削弱美国对乌克兰的支持，而中国的影响力活动旨在分裂美国人并削弱他们对民主的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/microsoft-sees-slowdown-in-russia-china-efforts-to-sway-us-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:51:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗破坏协议，美国将恢复对委内瑞拉的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-to-reimpose-venezuela-oil-ban-unless-maduro-acts-quickly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在确定尼古拉斯·马杜罗政权未能履行允许在定于 7 月举行的选举中进行更公平投票的协议后，总统乔·拜登政府重新对委内瑞拉实施石油制裁，结束了六个月的缓期执行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-to-reimpose-venezuela-oil-ban-unless-maduro-acts-quickly</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
